Manchester United beat Aston Villa 3-1 in the Premier League at Old Trafford on Saturday . 
  United moved up to third in the table with the win . 
  Ander Herrera opened the scoring for Louis van Gaal's side in the 43rd minute . 
  Wayne Rooney scored a stunning half-volley in the 79th minute to make it 2-0 . 
  Christian Benteke scored a consolation goal for Villa in the 80th minute . 
 